    {
        "index": 35,
        "tags": [],
        "content": "##  About us"
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "tags": [],
        "content": "We continually take the time to work with you personally to help you reach\nyour goals. We employ our proven CORE Principle to structure all study goals\nand exam formats, as well as learning and teaching methods, to make studying\nenjoyable and help you achieve the best possible outcome in your studies. In\ndoing so, our university received the Genius Loci Award for Excellence in\nTeaching from Stifterverband and the Volkswagen Foundation in 2018."
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "tags": [],
        "content": "At our University, you can choose from over 40 innovative degree programmes in\nthe areas of computer science, media and design, business administration,\nengineering and architecture, the social sciences, law, therapy and\npsychology. As one of the oldest and largest private universities in Germany,\nwe are part of a strong network of eight universities in all. Six SRH\nuniversities of applied sciences in Germany – in Berlin, Fürth, Gera,\nHeidelberg, North Rhine-Westphalia and Riedlingen – as well as SRH Paraguay\nand the EBS Universität für Wirtschaft und Recht in Wiesbaden Oestrich-Winkel."
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "tags": [],
        "content": "![\\\\\"Prof.](\\\\\"/fileadmin/_processed_/7/6/csm_Prof-Diener-Rektor-\nHSHD_0a9db082cb.jpg\\\\\")"
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "tags": [],
