    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "tags": [],
        "content": "Study according to the CORE Principle! Application-oriented learning in small\nteams, step-by-step skills development in five-week sprints and individual\nsupport from lecturers."
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "tags": [],
        "content": "Pure frontal teaching is not practised at SRH. Instead, our lecturers act as\nyour personal learning coaches. Together, you’ll not only delve into the\nsubject matter, but also hone your soft and hard skills. To do so, we rely on\ndirect communication. Personalised advice, digital exchange and regular\nfeedback are all very important to us."
